HEADWORD: Omnify
<hw>Om"ni*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Omni-</ets>
+ <ets>-fy</ets>.]</ety> <def>To render universal; to enlarge.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Omnify</qex> the disputed point into a transcendent, and you
may defy the opponent to lay hold of it.</q>
<rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Omnigenous</ent>⟦br⟧
